    },
    {
      "end": 25.260000228881836,
      "text": "I'm taken out of my final breath",
      "start": 19.239999771118164
    },
    {
      "end": 31.899999618530273,
      "text": "You took my heart again",
      "start": 25.260000228881836
    },
    {
      "end": 37.900001525878906,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 33.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 45.400001525878906,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 38.099998474121094
    },
    {
      "end": 53.97999954223633,
      "text": "I'm down, I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 46.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 60.08000183105469,
      "text": "There's no way you can see it",
      "start": 54.29999923706055
    },
    {
      "end": 63.15999984741211,
      "text": "I'm down for you",
      "start": 60.08000183105469
    },
    {
      "end": 66.33999633789062,
      "text": "I've been down to hustle out so many times",
      "start": 63.15999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 68.33999633789062,
      "text": "I can't understand my own song",
      "start": 66.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 70.58000183105469,
      "text": "Now you wanna write me a new one",
      "start": 68.33999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 73.68000030517578,
      "text": "You can pin my paddle left to right",
      "start": 70.87999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 78.05999755859375,
      "text": "And make me come and tell me the demons I fight in my own life",
      "start": 73.68000030517578
    },
    {
      "end": 81.77999877929688,
      "text": "Took my vulnerability and smashed me",
      "start": 78.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 85.30000305175781,
      "text": "When it took all my insecurities",
      "start": 81.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 87.77999877929688,
      "text": "Then you forced me to chill",
      "start": 85.37999725341797
    },
    {
      "end": 90.23999786376953,
      "text": "Now you got me too much",
      "start": 87.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 94.27999877929688,
      "text": "Well, I'm down to one last thing for you",
      "start": 90.23999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 101.30000305175781,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 95.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 108.69999694824219,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 102.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 113.73999786376953,
      "text": "Oh, the sight of you makes me want to be done",
      "start": 108.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 118.55999755859375,
      "text": "And have this be the last I see of you",
      "start": 113.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 126.0199966430664,
      "text": "Cause I'm down to just one breath",
      "start": 118.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 129.5399932861328,
      "text": "Darkness creeps in my mind",
      "start": 126.73999786376953
    },
    {
      "end": 132.4199981689453,
      "text": "Because you take away all the solid ego",
      "start": 129.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 135.05999755859375,
      "text": "That you had helped to build",
      "start": 132.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 140.83999633789062,
      "text": "Now you look like you want something else",
      "start": 135.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 143.83999633789062,
      "text": "Now I'm just a shell, baby",
      "start": 141.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 148.4199981689453,
      "text": "Kill me now, break me open and rip my insides",
      "start": 143.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 151.82000732421875,
      "text": "Cause no one wants a broken me",
      "start": 148.4199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 155.94000244140625,
      "text": "Now you make sure I've lost that spark",
      "start": 151.82000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 163.3800048828125,
      "text": "Cause I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 155.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 172.83999633789062,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath with you",
      "start": 165.36000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 179.3800048828125,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath for you",
      "start": 174.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 187,
      "text": "Oh, I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 180.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 191.94000244140625,
      "text": "As the sideways eats me down",
      "start": 187.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 195.75999450683594,
      "text": "As the blind ways feed me",
      "start": 191.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 200.32000732421875,
      "text": "From that love I said that I would give my own muse",
      "start": 195.75999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 203.9199981689453,
      "text": "I collectively wrap with me",
      "start": 200.32000732421875
    },
    {
      "end": 207.63999938964844,
      "text": "Off the balcony, one last breath",
      "start": 203.9199981689453
    },
    {
      "end": 211.22000122070312,
      "text": "See my eyes go black",
      "start": 207.63999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 217.8800048828125,
      "text": "I'm down, I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 211.24000549316406
    },
    {
      "end": 221.25999450683594,
      "text": "See me do the same",
      "start": 219.3800048828125
    },
    {
      "end": 224.8800048828125,
      "text": "See me do the things that you wanted me to be",
      "start": 221.25999450683594
    },
    {
      "end": 227.25999450683594,
      "text": "Me to be",
      "start": 225.55999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 231.9600067138672,
      "text": "See me do the architecture of the thing that I'm never free",
      "start": 227.27999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 234.8800048828125,
      "text": "From you and your mind",
      "start": 232.67999267578125
    },
    {
      "end": 237.83999633789062,
      "text": "Watch me die here",
      "start": 235.72000122070312
    },
    {
      "end": 241.94000244140625,
      "text": "The semblance of the thing that used to make you smile",
      "start": 237.83999633789062
    },
    {
      "end": 247.25999450683594,
      "text": "I'm down to one last breath",
      "start": 242.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 251.94000244140625,
      "text": "Moving by my own, baby, yeah",
      "start": 247.5399932861328
    },
    {
      "end": 257.2200012207031,
      "text": "Don't ever come back here no more, no more",
      "start": 252.89999389648438
    },
    {
      "end": 258.3599853515625,
      "text": "Jackie, get it?",
